Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.99,0:04:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,There it is! A storm is coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.00,0:04:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,We're ready for it! Bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.23,0:04:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, cool! It's getting windier and windier!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.50,0:04:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy, hold on to the flag!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.21,0:04:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's uncool for pirates to \Nhave their flag blown away!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.44,0:04:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright! Come on, wild wind!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.98,0:04:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, violent storm!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.48,0:04:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring it on, you bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.32,0:04:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Here it comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.86,0:04:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,--Luffy!\N--Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.33,0:04:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.23,0:04:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.83,0:04:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing, Luffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.00,0:04:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop laughing and help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.24,0:04:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Cool! We survived the storm!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.51,0:05:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,But the hideout's been destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.22,0:05:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's go and collect materials.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.62,0:05:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I want a telescope.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.79,0:05:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll never find that kind \Nof thing there, stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.69,0:05:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd rather find a cannon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.79,0:05:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It'd be cool if we could find one!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.37,0:05:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no good, Ace. I can't find a telescope.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.07,0:05:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy, we're not here for a telescope. \NLook for building materials.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.74,0:05:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe this is enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.32,0:05:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a telescope! Luffy's gonna be so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.33,0:05:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.66,0:05:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know that one of \Nthe three infamous brats
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.73,0:05:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,was from a noble family.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.07,0:05:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Bluejam! How did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.87,0:05:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, guys. But don't leave a mark on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.68,0:06:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you wanna fight?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.22,0:06:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Ace! Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.69,0:06:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,--I feel dizzy...\N--You okay, Sabo?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.69,0:06:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.69,0:06:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,If the three of us fight together, \Nwe can easily beat these fools!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.13,0:06:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right! We even beat \Nthe big tiger of Mt. Corvo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.86,0:06:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You little shits!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.10,0:06:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's just finish this up \Nby killing their captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.30,0:06:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.95,0:06:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.86,0:06:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, brats, don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.86,0:06:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not afraid of that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.07,0:06:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,--Damn! Let me go!\N--You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.73,0:07:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Go away! Or I'm gonna kick your butt!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.27,0:07:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me go, you bastard...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.38,0:07:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I barely made it in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.82,0:07:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.82,0:07:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,We didn't harm a hair on him, mister.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.99,0:07:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.73,0:07:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,--Damn! You...!\N--Sabo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.66,0:07:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,He wanted to find me so \Nbadly that he hired pirates?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.73,0:07:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,So they are the ones who \Ntempted Sabo into evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.20,0:07:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Give him back!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.54,0:07:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean "give him \Nback"? Sabo is my son.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.54,0:07:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Kids have to live as their parents say
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.45,0:07:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,because the parents brought \Nthem into the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.21,0:07:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you two tempt Sabo to run away?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.92,0:07:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You thug-wannabe brats!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.39,0:07:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you after my money?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.72,0:07:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.89,0:08:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, pirate! Be careful about hitting a kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.03,0:08:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got that trashy kid's blood all over me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.14,0:08:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.97,0:08:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Ack! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.64,0:08:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it! Nobody tempted me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.54,0:08:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I ran away of my own will!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.75,0:08:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You stay out of this! Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.75,0:08:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll leave the rest up to you, pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.39,0:08:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, mister. You've \Nalready paid us for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.56,0:08:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,We will take care of these two so \Nthey won't bother your boy again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.43,0:08:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute, Bluejam! \NDad, that's enough! I understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.04,0:08:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.74,0:08:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't do it, Sabo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.47,0:08:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do as you say. I'll \Nlive as you want so...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.15,0:08:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,...please don't hurt these two!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.85,0:08:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm begging you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.09,0:08:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,They're very important to \Nme, they're my brothers.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.22,0:09:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Sabo...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.26,0:09:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Then go home right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.96,0:09:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You should stop playing pirate. \NIt's just a waste of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.94,0:09:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Don't go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.70,0:09:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Be quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.27,0:09:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Sabo, run! You don't have to worry about us!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.01,0:09:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You said you wanna live freely with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.75,0:09:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Sabo, don't go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.38,0:09:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you gonna put an end to your dream?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.35,0:09:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Sabo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.42,0:09:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Sabo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.93,0:09:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Sabo!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.24,0:09:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain! What should we do with these kids?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.88,0:09:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,--Take them to our hideout.\N--Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.55,0:09:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You bastard! Untie me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.78,0:10:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Fight me again! I'm not gonna lose this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.05,0:10:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Be quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.49,0:10:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you bring us here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.92,0:10:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It must be nice to be a noble, \Ndon't you think so, brats?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.36,0:10:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,They look down on others as if they're \Ntrash and boss everyone around.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.73,0:10:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's such an easy life.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.67,0:10:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you think it's nice?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.64,0:10:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you getting at?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.64,0:10:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Being a pirate is way better! \NThat's what Sabo said!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.78,0:10:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm feeling bad for you \Nguys. Hey, untie them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.88,0:10:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.82,0:10:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you think a kid from a noble family
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.45,0:10:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,escaped to a place like Gray Terminal?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.06,0:10:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,He did it as a mockery of the people \Nhere just like noble adults do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.36,0:10:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet he was looking down on you guys, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.53,0:10:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not true! Sabo wouldn't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.90,0:10:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,He's right! We're brothers!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.24,0:10:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah? Alright, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.18,0:11:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,But you're not gonna bother \Nthat brat, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.15,0:11:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're planning on doing that,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.72,0:11:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd \Nhave to kill both of you right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.65,0:11:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,If you think of him as your brother, \Nit's best to leave him alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.02,0:11:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,For Sabo's good?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.09,0:11:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But Sabo hates High Town!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.60,0:11:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to let go of him if \Nyou really care about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.37,0:11:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll understand when you get older. And...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.57,0:11:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I had an axe to grind with you \Nabout what you did to Porchemy
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.08,0:11:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,but we can forget about it. I rather \Nliked your show of strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.95,0:11:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I wanted to ask you something. \NI think you might be interested.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.52,0:11:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm short-handed now. \NDo you guys wanna work for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.02,0:11:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's an easy task. \NIt's not dangerous at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.40,0:11:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,There is a map of Gray Terminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.93,0:12:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And you just have to carry packages \Nto the locations marked on the map.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.17,0:12:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you wanna do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.50,0:12:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.07,0:12:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,How much will you pay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.08,0:12:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Ace, I don't like it when Sabo is not around.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.15,0:12:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Live with it. I don't like it, \Neither. I wanna rescue Sabo.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.06,0:12:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't know what is really best for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.49,0:12:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see how things go. He's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.46,0:12:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,If he can't take it there, \Nhe can just come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.37,0:12:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's make some money for the \Npirate savings for that occasion.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.07,0:12:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't say it. It's not \NAce and Luffy's fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.88,0:12:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Why can't you tell the truth?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.91,0:12:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it because they warned \Nyou not to say anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.42,0:12:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,They're not those kinds of people!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.89,0:12:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,If you have a criminal record, it \Ndamages your family's reputation
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.99,0:12:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,and you can't enter High Town.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.83,0:13:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You were tempted by those two,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.23,0:13:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,having no choice but to \Nget involved in violence,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.07,0:13:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,weren't you, Sabo?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.81,0:13:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Sabo.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.07,0:13:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The fate of your friends in Gray Terminal
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.41,0:13:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,is in the hands of those pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.31,0:13:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And I can give them an order.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.01,0:13:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,If they're that important to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.42,0:13:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,think about what you have to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.69,0:13:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a smart boy. \NYou know what you should do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.96,0:13:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You promised that you wouldn't hurt them!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.53,0:13:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I came back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.50,0:13:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,A crime is a crime! We did \Nit of our own free will...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.67,0:13:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.24,0:13:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so sad to have such a stupid son!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.98,0:13:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you understand my dilemma?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.25,0:13:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it must be so hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.22,0:14:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take care of the papers.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.54,0:14:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.44,0:14:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, Sabo, let's go. It's been \Na long while since you left.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.81,0:14:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, don't go in yet - you're filthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.55,0:14:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Wash and disinfect your \Nbody in the yard first.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.39,0:14:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Then take a bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.36,0:14:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad that you're safe, young master.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.69,0:14:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Sabo! You're back. You got bigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.43,0:14:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.40,0:14:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Now Stelly, say "hi" to your older brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.67,0:14:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you, brother! \NMy name is Stelly and I'm 8.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.11,0:14:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.78,0:14:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,We adopted him. He's a smart \Nboy from a noble family.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.55,0:15:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,But for some reason, his \Nparents became negligent.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.39,0:15:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,And we took him in since \Nhe's full of promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.99,0:15:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't work out to be my successor...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.26,0:15:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm telling you too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.37,0:15:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Go to your room now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.83,0:15:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to start studying tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.31,0:15:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you gonna put an end to your dream?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.02,0:15:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, brother! I heard that \Nyou're pretty stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.46,0:15:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother and father were always \Nsaying that behind the curtain.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.33,0:15:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But you have the devil's luck
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.80,0:15:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,'cuz they're gonna take care of \Nthe burnables tomorrow night.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.37,0:15:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,If you had stayed in Gray Terminal,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.27,0:15:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,you would've died tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.01,0:16:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it would've been better for me
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.38,0:16:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,if their real son didn't come home...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.48,0:16:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,W-W-What are you doing?! I'll tell father!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.38,0:16:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What were you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.22,0:16:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on? Tell me everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.76,0:16:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-There's gonna be a fire in Gray Terminal tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.03,0:16:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,--A fire?!\N--Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.10,0:16:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't know about \Nit because you weren't here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.30,0:16:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,But they decided it months ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.34,0:16:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you know that the World Government
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.40,0:16:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,has sent a group of observers \Nto go around the East Blue?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.71,0:16:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,They're gonna arrive in Goa \NKingdom finally 3 days from now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.05,0:16:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And they have a World Noble,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.78,0:16:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,a Celestial Dragon with them \Nso people are panicking!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.95,0:16:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The members of the royal family \Ndon't want him to see our stigma,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.06,0:16:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,so they decided to burn down Gray Terminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.16,0:16:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Then this country will be clean!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.23,0:16:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking \Nabout? That's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.37,0:17:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,There are a lot of people living there!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.07,0:17:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,They can't take away their home!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.44,0:17:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.14,0:17:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Weren't you listening to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.71,0:17:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,They're gonna burn up all \Nthe shame of this country.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.35,0:17:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean, the people, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.06,0:17:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.50,0:17:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.14,0:17:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't just jump down...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.38,0:17:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It is not my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.05,0:17:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a lie! He must be lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.55,0:17:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not possible to burn \Ndown an area so large!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.96,0:17:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,They were from this afternoon...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.49,0:18:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Are we ready for tomorrow? \NThere can't be any miscalculation.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.33,0:18:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,We're ready but the unknown \Nfactor is the pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.23,0:18:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,They have to burn the trash precisely.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.81,0:18:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Bluejam's clan is setting \Nboxes of oil and explosives...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.31,0:18:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,...all over Gray Terminal up until the appointed time tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.25,0:18:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Bluejam has a hand in this? \NThen it must be true!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.98,0:18:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's so ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.76,0:18:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder how's Sabo doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.47,0:18:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up and go to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.60,0:18:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,We agreed to let go of Sabo for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.81,0:18:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.81,0:18:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,This could be better for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.28,0:18:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Sabo...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.41,0:18:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.22,0:18:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Telescope...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.38,0:19:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I can figure out if there'll be a fire or not
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.48,0:19:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,by the look of people in the town.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.05,0:19:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,--Hi, good morning!\N--Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.12,0:19:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,--Isn't it a lovely morning.\N--Yes, it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.56,0:19:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh great! There is nothing wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.66,0:19:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll walk around the town.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.63,0:19:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow morning should be \Nmore lovely, shouldn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.87,0:19:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it should.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.88,0:20:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything seems normal as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.79,0:20:04.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Today is windy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.99,0:20:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, indeed, your Majesty.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.32,0:20:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Accidents could easily happen on a \Nday like this - especially fires.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.60,0:20:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right, your Majesty.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.73,0:20:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Sabo is not in the house?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.44,0:20:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,He's such a spoiled brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.54,0:20:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,He still wants to keep playing \Npirate without studying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.41,0:20:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Search the whole town!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.65,0:20:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,He can't have gotten out \Nof the town so easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.45,0:20:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,--Excuse me, mister.\N--What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.72,0:20:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know that there'll be a fire in Gray Terminal tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.56,0:20:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, I know. What about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.06,0:20:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,He knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.53,0:20:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Which family are you from?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.30,0:20:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.27,0:20:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.70,0:20:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on here? \NEverybody knows about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.91,0:21:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,They all know about it and \Nthey're acting normally?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.74,0:21:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't anyone care about the fire in Gray Terminal?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.18,0:21:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, there you are, you brats.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.42,0:21:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want us to carry the boxes?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.69,0:21:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, and there will be a \Nbig task for you tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.09,0:21:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.10,0:21:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad knows about it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.70,0:21:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why he brought me \Nback - before the fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.71,0:21:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Because he wants me to maintain their status
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.21,0:21:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,and inherit their property even \Nthough he thinks I'm a fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.88,0:21:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry if my dog is bothering you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.09,0:21:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You're out of breath. What's the matter, boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.19,0:21:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.76,0:21:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah? Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.83,0:21:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Do you know that there'll be a fire in Gray Terminal tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.13,0:21:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.30,0:22:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Why doesn't anyone in this town \Nincluding you look concerned?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.51,0:22:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Why does no one try to prevent it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.61,0:22:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You sound like you're a kind boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.15,0:22:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,But, listen carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.12,0:22:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,We all have to keep quiet about the plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.15,0:22:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What if someone outside the \Ntown finds out about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.49,0:22:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We're special! If you're \Nfrom a noble family...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.83,0:22:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.23,0:22:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Ace! Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.64,0:22:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,There's something wrong \Nwith this town! Everybody's crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.21,0:22:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though they know that \Npeople will die soon,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.28,0:22:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,they act normally and even smile!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.68,0:22:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't wanna stay here! \NI gotta tell them quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.09,0:22:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Today of all days, it's windy!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.59,0:22:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,There he is! Isn't it him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.19,0:22:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no doubt! That's the runaway boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.26,0:22:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey you, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.46,0:23:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The people in this country \Nare planning to burn up
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.47,0:23:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,their national shame tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.44,0:23:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to get out of the \NGray Terminal! Ace! Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.61,0:23:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Run! Ace! Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.55,0:23:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,After learning the secret \Nbehind the fire outbreak,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.45,0:23:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy and Ace are pushed into \Ndire straits by Bluejam.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.82,0:23:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Sabo rushes into Gray Terminal to save them,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.50,0:23:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,but the intensely burning flames
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.10,0:23:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,are about to devour Luffy and Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.77,0:23:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time, on One Piece:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.24,0:23:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,"The Fire's Been Set \NGray Terminal in Crisis"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.04,0:23:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be the Pirate King!!
